## Poly.keys() function

Returns a [PolySyncIterable](./polyethylene.polysynciterable.md) that yields the same elements as `Object.keys` would.

**Signature:**

```typescript
function keys<K extends string | number | symbol>(obj: Record<K, unknown>): PolySyncIterable<K>;
```
